{"tid":755530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"個條柒頭呀勇真係唔抵可憐","createTime":"2018-07-25T09:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T16:26:07.000Z","uid":181819,"like":55,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"17c0fe79d0423a1a3020f04ca27d8b9bcb12a245","tid":755530,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T09:42:18.000Z","msg":"其實大家無必要同無責任去幫佢討回公道<br />\n<br />\n首先一樣野佢本身個人都動機不良：上網識人根本就係有咁既風險，正如一個後生女上網識人比人姦左，口臭如屎既連登仔都唔會有絲毫同情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢只係狗公得黎又食唔到人 反而比人食返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有喂屌你比人呃左50萬都未撚醒 呢條友算狗掃把啦無可救藥 可能係佢眼中呢D係愛一個人既付出 咁咪由鳩佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總結黎講 話佢狗公佢又蠢過豬 話佢善良佢又動機不純<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31fd394a0f4f0693a7c3c5d2011b48386b38715","tid":755530,"uid":162539,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T09:43:55.000Z","msg":"無人可憐佢，根本個個食花生想睇所有人都仆街"},{"pid":"ea34f8028abdb0c636e84158101cea3047a4dead","tid":755530,"uid":176366,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T09:45:28.000Z","msg":"呃人應該 <br />\n俾人呃係抵死戇鳩智撚障<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主啲價值觀都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d574c364b8af45f3b2f9f5e7132236313a0582","tid":755530,"uid":181819,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"ea34f8028abdb0c636e84158101cea3047a4dead","tid":755530,"uid":176366,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTim